<h2>Your Account Has Been Temporarily Locked</h2>

<p>Dear <%= @user.full_name.presence || @user.email_address %>,</p>

<p>We've detected suspicious activity on your account and have temporarily locked it as a security precaution.</p>

<h3>What happened?</h3>
<p>Our security system detected unusual activity patterns that may indicate unauthorized access attempts. To protect your account, we've temporarily suspended access.</p>

<h3>What should you do?</h3>
<ol>
  <li>Your account will be automatically unlocked at <strong><%= @unlock_time.strftime("%I:%M %p on %B %d, %Y") %></strong></li>
  <li>If you believe this was triggered by your own activity, you can wait for the automatic unlock</li>
  <li>If you did not trigger this activity, please contact our support team immediately</li>
  <li>Consider changing your password once your account is unlocked</li>
</ol>

<h3>Security Tips:</h3>
<ul>
  <li>Use a strong, unique password for your account</li>
  <li>Enable two-factor authentication if available</li>
  <li>Be cautious of phishing emails asking for your credentials</li>
  <li>Always sign in from secure, trusted devices</li>
</ul>

<p>If you need immediate assistance or believe your account has been compromised, please contact our support team.</p>

